data.description: Look no farther!! Beautifully remodeled turn-of-the-century multi-level home is turn-key ready. 5 bedrooms (2 non-conforming), and 3 bathrooms spread over 3 levels. Main level is perfect for entertaining with an open-style flow through the sun porch, into the living room, through the dining room, then into the kitchen and straight through to the adorable backyard. Basement has private entrance, could potentially become income producing apartment. Too beautiful for the photos, come take a look! Call Amber Pearson at 406-750-2648, or your real estate professional.
